BADGE_DESCRIPTION: Change your badge on the server
CHATBOT_ADD_DESCRIPTION: Add a chatbot to the server
CHATBOT_REMOVE_DESCRIPTION: Remove a chatbot from the server
COLOR_DESCRIPTION: Change your color on the server
EMOTE_ADD_DESCRIPTION: Add an emote to the server
EMOTE_REMOVE_DESCRIPTION: Remove an emote from the server
FAKE_DESCRIPTION: Send a message faking being someone else
INTERVAL_DESCRIPTION: Time interval. Choose between day, week, month, year, or all time
MATCH_DESCRIPTION: Match profile pictures of two users
RANKING_DESCRIPTION: Get the ranking of message counts from server members
STICKER_ADD_DESCRIPTION: Add a sticker to the server
STICKER_REMOVE_DESCRIPTION: Remove a sticker from the server
SUMMARIZE_DESCRIPTION: See a summary of the latest messages discussed in the channel
UNDO_DELETE_DESCRIPTION: Undo the last deletion or edit of a message in the channel (up to 5 minutes)
UPTIME_DESCRIPTION: Check how long the bot has been online
VERTICAL_DESCRIPTION: Should the profile pictures be joined vertically?
